        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Free Time Sheet Calculator</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Stop losing money to manual math errors. Calculate your weekly hours, breaks, overtime, and gross pay instantly with our...</p>
